Brand: VTECH MOTOR

VTECH MOTOR Co., LTD. was established in Dec. of 2003, located in Hsinchu County, Taiwan; Mainly producing various of automotive and motorcycle FUEL PUMP and Motors; Currently supply FUEL PUMP to TOYOTA / HOTAI Group, FORD Motor and Mazda in service parts OES supply system;
Our Join Venture Mother company called Chi- Hua Fitness Co., LTD. (stock no.: 1593)- is striving in Design, Research & Development of Generator Brake and Motors, and has German, American and Japanese national patents;

Since foundation, VTECH MOTOR were actively engaged penetration of global markets, new model development, searching for better material and suppliers to provide customers more professional & effective services; We received local market's supports and approval, will stand here, expand Taiwan's international quality level of producing motors to overseas and created value for global competition;

Currently, VTECH MOTOR had automatically rotor production line, our main products includes Fuel pumps and Radiator fan motors ... etc; Brush less Motors and B/S Reducing Motors are in our new developing projects;
